attributes.title: Should I Bring a Dildo? - HOW TO RTX
attributes.caption: In this episode of our classic show How To RTX, we play a game of Prop Hunt with Adam, and explain what we'll be going at RTX and beyond!
attributes.description: In this episode of our classic show How To RTX, we play a game of Prop Hunt with Adam, and explain what we'll be going at RTX and beyond!   Our show How To RTX has been running for 37 years, and has the distinction of being the longest-running web series of all time. Past multi-episode arcs have included the Kovic/Greene wedding, Lawrence's demon possession, the series where Spoole discovered his real mother, Joel's touching trip to Ibiza, and a very special episode dealing with James' crippling heroin addiction.   Yes, it's been quite a ride for How To RTX: THE SERIES!, but I really think that this is probably our best episode of this long-running show ever.
attributes.display_title: Should I Bring a Dildo? - HOW TO RTX

attributes.title: OFFICE WET DREAMS
attributes.caption: ​I swear, this is the final office tour video we'll do. Hopefully.
attributes.description: I swear, this is the final office tour video we'll do. Hopefully.Since we've joined Rooster Teeth, we've had 3 offices, with 3 office moves. You've been with us through Herzog and the Uwe Boll. You were there for the Wallocaust. And now you're finally here for....I guess we don't have a name for this office now.Either way, this better be the last time we move. Lawrence's back is getting pretty tweaked from lugging our c-stands all over the place. Honestly, though, I'm playing it safe. Keeping one of my moving boxes packed, just in case we have to get up and go again.In which case you can look forward to yet another office tour.

attributes.title: ANOTHER Animated Show!? Funhaus Cartoons
attributes.description: This is the original pilot episode for Funhaus Cartoons! Yeah, I know what you're thinking: a sincere video description WTF is wrong with Funhaus I don't know. Maybe we're just excited about the new show. Maybe we had a change of heart. Maybe little happy parasites got into our brains and are filling us with general goodwill.Regardless, our plan is for Funhaus Cartoons to air monthly, at the end of each month. We're going to premiere the first episode on October 31 (SPOOOOKY), and go from there. We really hope you like the style and tone as much as we do!

attributes.title: FART BUTTON - Funhaus Cartoons
attributes.caption: Welcome to a brave new show, unlike anything you've ever seen before. A fantastic world of -- oh wait, it's just another animated show on the Internet.
attributes.description: Welcome to a brave new show, unlike anything you've ever seen before. A fantastic world of -- oh wait, it's just another animated show on the Internet.EXCEPT THIS ONE HAS FUNHAUS IN IT!Yup, it's our new show, Funhaus Cartoons. We really hope you like this bad boy, we've been working on it for a while with our animator, Andy. Here are a few things we'd like to see in future episodes:1080p (seriously, SHOULD be coming next episode)More Joel (really ought to be #1 on this list)Lens flare, lens flare, lens flare (sent in notes to Andy about this one)Animated Chizzywick (actually wrote this as a joke, but maybe we should do this 4real)Accurate representation of sentient tumors on Spoole's neck (Barry and Larry)Subliminal messaging ("Buy more tshirts")90-minute episodes (pending $74,998,000 budget increase)Let us know what you think in the comments!

attributes.title: MASTER CHIEF LOVES PRINCESS LEIA
attributes.caption: So, Microsoft sent us a limited edition Halo 5 Xbox.  We were all like, "Hey, cool! But most of us have Xboxes already, and Joel doesn't love console games. What should we do with this thing?"
attributes.description: So, Microsoft sent us a limited edition Halo 5 Xbox.We were all like, "Hey, cool! But most of us have Xboxes already, and Joel doesn't love console games. What should we do with this thing" Then we hit on it: let's give it away to someone. You're welcome.End of post.Oh, right, we should tell you what's going on.Here's the deal: we wrote some really dumb fan fiction, and then made it into a video. Your job is to make a Fan Art poster of our dumb fan fiction. And then our job is to select what we think is the best one and give the winning artist an Xbox!Rules and dumb stuff:1) Submit your photos as reply comments in this thread. Upload the picture to your RT profile (or a site like Imgur) and copy that image URL as your comment.2) Winner must have a shipping address in the United States (sorrrrry!!)3) No steal other people's submission or artwork. No pr0n. Be cool please.
